Description copied from interface: Outputter
Prepare to output a record. The parameters given here will be active until endRecord is called. See the note on thread safety for this interface.

Specified by:
startRecord in interface Outputter
Parameters:

transmitterBootTime - the transmitter's boot time (for this connection).
seqNo - the sequence number of the record. Usually, this increases each time, but there may be occasions when the sequence number starts back at a lower value or skips.
